{"type":null,"faqId":44508,"title":"如何开启 GPS 定位？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>打开下拉通知栏，点击 GPS 的快捷开关，可快速打开或关闭 GPS 卫星定位。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果想导航定位更精确或更省电，可进入手机设置界面，点击定位服务或位置信息访问权限，根据需要选择不同的定位方法，如使用 WLAN、移动网络或 AGPS 等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159329\" style=\"width:1.6138889in;height:2.8659723in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159330\" style=\"width:1.6138889in;height:2.8631945in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159331\" style=\"width:1.6138889in;height:2.8631945in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400819000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":17,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0